              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "6-C-12",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.989
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Vitreous carbon with a density of",
                "1.54 g/cm3 and thickness of 149.4 mg/cm2 located at",
                "the midacceptance target position of the A1900",
                "fragment separator",
                "Be target with thickness of 188 mg/cm2"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Target position was surrounded by the high-",
                "resolution gamma-ray detection system SeGA, an array",
                "of 32-fold segmented high-purity germanium detectors",
                "with high degree of segmentation which allowed for",
                "event-by-event Doppler reconstruction of the gamma rays",
                "emitted by the projectile-like reaction residues",
                "in flight."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Reaction products were momentum analyzed by",
                "magnetic spectrograph S800."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Event-by-event particle identification",
                "was performed with the focal-plane detection system",
                "formed by ionization chamber, which measured energy",
                "loss and plastic scintillation detector for",
                "time-of-flight measurement."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC",
                "COINC",
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Coincidence of the reaction product",
                "                 and discrete gamma ray was required"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "KINDT"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The projectile beam of 22Mg was obtained by",
                "projectile fragmentation of a 170-MeV per nucleon",
                "24Mg primary beam. The 9Be fragmentation target of",
                "1904 mg/cm2 thickness was located at the midacceptance",
                "target position of the A1900 fragment separator. The",
                "momentum acceptance of the separator was restricted",
                "to dp/p = 0.0014. The resulting cocktail beam of N=10",
                "isotones contained 22Mg (74%), 21Na (24.5%), and",
                "20Ne (1.5%)."
              ]
            }
          ],
